`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Steal
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * Steal <target>

 It allows items to be stolen from the inventory of mobs and characters. Be
warned that steal is an aggressive skill, and if failed or noticed, you will be
attacked by the target you're trying to steal from.

